message.body: Heya Heya, Rae is apparently going out of town for weekend and wondered if Tues is ok for cat pickup. Let me know if that's too late though and I'll see if he can arrange something or if I can find an alt weekend home for her. Know next week is super busy but maybe we can grab a coffee or drink or something. Xo m
No, it's cool just whenever it works out. Coffee/drink sounds good. Hopefully bouffant b.o. on Saturday too.
Ok thanks, appreciate the patience. And great about out bev and BB. Till soon then! Hope today was productive!
